	<div class="posts">
	<a name="92016950">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<a href="http://www.osnews.com/story.php?news_id=2997">Interview with the KDE and Gnome UI/Usability Developers - OSNews.com</a>.&nbsp; A peak at OSnews, and a site devoted to operating-system initiatives, etc.  This discussion of where desktops are going, and how they are being componentized is intriguing.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#92016950">Friday, April 04, 2003</a></span></div>
